OL,6,FOne of the UK's most wanted men who
OL,7,Fspent four years on the run has
OL,8,Fadmitted conspiring to supply cocaine
OL,9,Fin Wales.
OL,11,FCalvin Parris, 34, from Cardiff, was
OL,12,Fdetained by police in Portugal near
OL,13,Fthe town of Boliqueime on the Algarve
