OL,3,COne of UK's most wanted men who spent
OL,4,Cyears on the run admits cocaine charge
OL,6,FHe was brought back to Wales by the
OL,7,FNational Crime Agency (NCA) after
OL,8,Fspending four years on the run, and
OL,9,Fpleaded guilty to one count of
OL,10,Fconspiring to supply cocaine at
OL,11,FCardiff Crown Court on Thursday, 12
OL,12,FDecember.
OL,14,FThe court heard that he was suspected
OL,15,Fof being a customer of a highly-
OL,16,Forganised crime group which brought
OL,17,F46kg of cocaine with a street value of
OL,18,F#8million into Wales between February
OL,19,Fand June 2020.
