OL,3,COne of UK's most wanted men who spent
OL,4,Cyears on the run admits cocaine charge
OL,6,FIt is believed that the group used
OL,7,Fencrypted communication devices
OL,8,Foperating on the 'EncroChat' platform
OL,9,Fto traffic the class A drugs into
OL,10,Fsouth Wales.
OL,12,FThe 34-year-old, known for his row of
OL,13,Fgold front teeth, appeared at Cardiff
OL,14,FCrown Court via video link wearing a
OL,15,FNike sports top, and spoke only to
OL,16,Fconfirm his name and enter his guilty
OL,17,Fplea.
