OL,3,COne of UK's most wanted men who spent
OL,4,Cyears on the run admits cocaine charge
OL,6,FThe court heard that the National
OL,7,FCrime Agency believe he is the final
OL,8,Fmember of the organised crime group.
OL,9,FHe is due to be sentenced on 14
OL,10,FFebruary, 2025, at Merthyr Tydfil
OL,11,FCrown Court.
OL,13,FParris had been named as one of the
OL,14,FNCA's most wanted fugitives after
OL,15,Fgoing on the run in November 2020.
